org.nasdanika.codegen.ecore.web.ui.model

Interface EAttributeConfiguration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CDOObject, CDOWithID, EModelElementConfiguration, ENamedElementConfiguration, EObject, EStructuralFeatureConfiguration, ETypedElementConfiguration, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EAttributeConfigurationImpl

    public interface EAttributeConfiguration
extends EStructuralFeatureConfiguration

    A representation of the model object ‘EAttribute Configuration’.

    The following features are supported:

    • Format
    • Choices
    • Html
    See Also:
    ModelPackage.getEAttributeConfiguration()

      • getFormat

        String getFormat()

        Returns the value of the ‘Format’ attribute. Format is used for rendering and parsing date and number feature values. SimpleDateFormat for dates, DecimalFormat for numbers.

        Returns:
        the value of the ‘Format’ attribute.

      • isHtml

        boolean isHtml()

        Returns the value of the ‘Html’ attribute. If control is textarea and html is set to true then the textarea is initialized with TinyMCE editor.

        the value of the ‘Html’ attribute.
